# Break-Glass Exception Log

This file tracks all emergency governance bypass events for audit and compliance.

## Log Format

### Emergency Break-Glass (Type 4 Exceptions)
```
---
Date: [ISO 8601 timestamp]
Incident: #[incident-number]
PR: #[pr-number]
Authorizers: [name1, name2]
Bypass Type: [merge-without-approval / force-push / ci-skip / etc]
Duration: [start-timestamp] to [end-timestamp]
Impact: [brief description]
Rollback Executed: [yes/no]
Post-Incident Review: [link or "pending"]
---
```

### Standard Review Exceptions (Type 1-3)
```
---
Date: [ISO 8601 timestamp]
Exception Type: [Type-1 / Type-2 / Type-3]
PR: #[pr-number]
Title: [PR title]
Approver: [Name (Role)]
Justification: [Brief reason]
Impact Scope: [Production / Staging / Development]
Risk Level: [Low / Medium / High]
Post-Merge Actions: [List of follow-up actions]
Completed: [yes / no / N/A]
---
```

